Home
Learn About Us
It's a pretty
special
place
We are a 55+ community, perfectly located in sunny central Florida, where you can strive each day to lead an active, meaningful and happy life. Our vision was to create a community with the ideal backdrop for you to write the next chapter of your story, a place where you can grow, learn new things, and spend more time doing the things you love surrounded by friends who are more like family.
In our hometown, each of our Villages are made up of a collection of quaint neighborhoods surrounded by a wide variety of recreation, golf, entertainment, shopping, dining, and wellness opportunities – just a golf car ride away. Go exploring and have a new adventure every day.  Reconnect with family and make new friends. In The Villages, your dreams can become a reality.
We invite you to experience life in
Florida’s Friendliest Hometown!
Come Visit
Free Information Catalog
The
heart
of it all
Located in the heart of central Florida, we believe everything you need to live life to the fullest is right here in our hometown. You can easily get anywhere you want to go by automobile or golf car, plus we are convenient for all your friends and family to come visit you in Florida’s Friendliest Hometown.

Meet Our Team
Meet Our Team
Properties of The Villages Real Estate Professionals are happy to serve the needs of both current and future Villagers. We believe our commitment to excellence in customer service with our extensive knowledge of this community, makes us the best partner to serve your needs.
We'd
love
to show you around
Find Your Real Estate Professional
In addition to being licensed Florida real estate agents, our team of over 350 representatives receives frequent training beyond the state’s continuing education requirements. These topics include hands-on home product knowledge, customer care, and the latest information about The Villages lifestyle that we all enjoy.
Most importantly, whether you’re purchasing your next dream home, or selling your current one, our team shares a sincere commitment to put your needs first… always!
